Description
The current monitoring documentation suggests an approach that is defunct. This PR refreshes our recommendations on this topic.
@JimGalasyn One consideration that we may want to make is mirroring this page in our enterprise docs, but also describing how to set up with on a tar/rpm package, etc. In that case, all you need to do is export a JMX_PORT variable without supplying more configuration.
